---
title: Chickpea & Avocado Burrito Bowl with Leafy Rice & Coriander
description: Embark on a culinary fiesta with our Mexican burrito bowl, where chickpeas are simmered in a tomato-based sauce and served alongside a mild avocado salsa and cooling sour cream. This vibrant bowl is a symphony of flavours, delivering a taste of Mexico in every satisfying bite!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/672d69d31cd01ca44ffc081c-128d41b9.jpeg
